{"id":233353,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/06/维权网-发课公司税案开庭，多人被限制自由，两/","date":"2012-06-20T09:31:07Z","modified":"2012-06-20T09:31:07Z","title":"维权网 | 发课公司税案开庭，多人被限制自由，两百人现场围观（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-V9lrrhT2sC0/T-GF-srfo0I/AAAAAAAAInY/JlUwpkhIa6E/s1600/%E4%B8%89%E5%9B%9B%E5%90%8D%E5%9B%BD%E4%BF%9D%E6%92%95%E6%89%AF%E5%8F%91%E8%AF%BE%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%91%98%E5%B7%A5%EF%BC%8C%E6%91%84%E5%83%8F%E6%9C%BA%E6%8D%9F%E6%AF%81_files.jpg\"></a><br /><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-V9lrrhT2sC0/T-GF-srfo0I/AAAAAAAAInY/JlUwpkhIa6E/s1600/%E4%B8%89%E5%9B%9B%E5%90%8D%E5%9B%BD%E4%BF%9D%E6%92%95%E6%89%AF%E5%8F%91%E8%AF%BE%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%91%98%E5%B7%A5%EF%BC%8C%E6%91%84%E5%83%8F%E6%9C%BA%E6%8D%9F%E6%AF%81_files.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"214\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-V9lrrhT2sC0/T-GF-srfo0I/AAAAAAAAInY/JlUwpkhIa6E/s320/%E4%B8%89%E5%9B%9B%E5%90%8D%E5%9B%BD%E4%BF%9D%E6%92%95%E6%89%AF%E5%8F%91%E8%AF%BE%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%91%98%E5%B7%A5%EF%BC%8C%E6%91%84%E5%83%8F%E6%9C%BA%E6%8D%9F%E6%AF%81_files.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>国保撕扯发课公司员工，摄像机损毁（王仲夏推特图片）</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-ghgVv4ZYcXg/T-GGEDwTKHI/AAAAAAAAIng/4C7D1owtS-k/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"218\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-ghgVv4ZYcXg/T-GGEDwTKHI/AAAAAAAAIng/4C7D1owtS-k/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>陈云飞等人现场声援（刘艳萍推特图片）</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-C-e6KpwD3ok/T-GGGCrlF0I/AAAAAAAAIno/WNRbHtlEjio/s1600/Avz_sfWCMAAYa6H.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-C-e6KpwD3ok/T-GGGCrlF0I/AAAAAAAAIno/WNRbHtlEjio/s320/Avz_sfWCMAAYa6H.jpg\" width=\"219\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员郑毅报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>点</span><span>，发课公司诉北京市地税局第二稽查局一案在朝阳法院开庭。艾未未等多名异见人士因此被限制人身自由，庭审现场有两百名网友围观声援，除了发课公司法人路青、律师及会计师出庭外，无人能够申请到旁听证。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据本网了解，发课公司代理、与发课公司涉税案有直接关系的艾未未被禁止到法庭并被限制人身自由，为了阻止异见人士到法院声援关注，刘晓原律师被国保带往北京郊区怀柔软禁，许志永、江天勇、王荔蕻、莫之许、吴玉仁、刘荻等人被限制人身自由。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>在法庭尚未开庭的上午，三十余辆警车、百余名警察将北京草场地</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">258</span><span>号包围，艾未未工作室人员被警察推搡受伤，摄像机被抢夺。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>下午两点左右，朝阳法院门口，有大量便衣及警察在现场监控。更有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>条公交线路甩站，在朝阳法院附近不停车。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>艾未未工作室员工刘艳萍向本网信息员表示：围观者目测有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">200</span><span>人左右，非常多的便衣和警察，只要外媒记者一出现就马上被警察带走。发课公司法人曾申请旁听证，但被告知没有位置。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>前往现场声援的陈云飞说：现场有两百多名声援者，警车有上百辆，外国记者在几百米外就被拦截阻止采访。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>在法庭外，有维权人士手举“法律无尊严，百姓无人权”；“没有抗争，就没有改变”的标牌，以示对艾未未和发课公司的支持。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\n<p><span>下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>点，庭审仍未结束，支持者与监控者都在等候审判结果。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-8Ha_7wqjfY8/T-GJXX5hsTI/AAAAAAAAIn4/dqEr4YZP0q4/s1600/4.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"640\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-8Ha_7wqjfY8/T-GJXX5hsTI/AAAAAAAAIn4/dqEr4YZP0q4/s640/4.jpg\" width=\"241\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-6339570279538624193?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/06/8e692691E59BBE00.jpg-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[19196,9625]}